org.framed.orm.model

Interface Shape

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModelElement, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ShapeImpl

    public interface Shape
extends ModelElement
    A representation of the model object 'Shape'.

    The following features are supported:

    • First Segment
    • Second Segment
    • Model
    • Description
    • Boundaries

    See Also:
    OrmPackage.getShape()
